335
00:32:46,131 --> 00:32:48,008
<font color=#FFFF00>Lave-se, coma algo.</font>

336
00:32:48,008 --> 00:32:49,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Deixa comigo.</font>

337
00:32:54,390 --> 00:32:55,766
<font color=#FFFF00>Está bem.</font>

338
00:32:56,392 --> 00:32:57,685
<font color=#FFFF00>- Obrigada.
