344
00:34:11,425 --> 00:34:13,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Aonde pensa que está indo?</font>

345
00:34:13,343 --> 00:34:15,054
<font color=#FFFF00>O que espera que eu faça?</font>

346
00:34:15,054 --> 00:34:18,098
